data.description: This fantastic three bedroom home conveniently located in Fresno is ready to be sold. This cozy property has updated flooring, an open floor plan, and a comfortable layout. The property is only minutes away from the fantastic restaurants, businesses, and events. The home also has a very usable back yard with a lot of potential. There is a two car garage with a long drive way and potential RV parking.
